    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "The credibility assessment team reviewed all 13 V&V 40 factors. Twelve of thirteen factors meet or exceed their required levels. The Test conditions factor achieves level 2 against a required level of 3; however, the team judged that the single ASTM F1717 configuration is the only clinically relevant scenario for this specific device and submission context, and that the remaining factor evidence collectively supports a Medium assurance level. The model is accepted for the stated COU.",
